## 🔒 Security & Data Compliance Note
All XML structures, pipeline flows, and field configurations in this repository are strictly sanitized.
*   **No Real Data:** Contains no real job requisitions, candidate names, personal phone numbers, or corporate tenant URLs.
*   **Safe IP Usage:** Templates leverage standard SAP SuccessFactors technical tags and dummy field criteria to demonstrate functional and technical mastery without exposing client property.

